280   private static int zzUnpackAction(String packed, int offset, int [] result) {
281     int i = 0;       /* index in packed string  */
282     int j = offset;  /* index in unpacked array */
283     int l = packed.length();
284     while (i < l) {
285       int count = packed.charAt(i++);
286       int value = packed.charAt(i++);
287       do result[j++] = value; while (--count > 0);
288     }
289     return j;
290   }

671   private static int zzUnpackRowMap(String packed, int offset, int [] result) {
672     int i = 0;  /* index in packed string  */
673     int j = offset;  /* index in unpacked array */
674     int l = packed.length();
675     while (i < l) {
676       int high = packed.charAt(i++) << 16;
677       result[j++] = high | packed.charAt(i++);
678     }
679     return j;
680   }

6637   private static int [] zzUnpackTrans() {
6638     int [] result = new int[235368];
6639     int offset = 0;
6640     offset = zzUnpackTrans(ZZ_TRANS_PACKED_0, offset, result);
6641     offset = zzUnpackTrans(ZZ_TRANS_PACKED_1, offset, result);
6642     offset = zzUnpackTrans(ZZ_TRANS_PACKED_2, offset, result);
6643     return result;
6644   }
6645 
6646   private static int zzUnpackTrans(String packed, int offset, int [] result) {
6647     int i = 0;       /* index in packed string  */
6648     int j = offset;  /* index in unpacked array */
6649     int l = packed.length();
6650     while (i < l) {
6651       int count = packed.charAt(i++);
6652       int value = packed.charAt(i++);
6653       value--;
6654       do result[j++] = value; while (--count > 0);
6655     }
6656     return j;
6657   }

6715   private static int zzUnpackAttribute(String packed, int offset, int [] result) {
6716     int i = 0;       /* index in packed string  */

6723     }
6724     return j;

6846   /** 
6847    * Unpacks the compressed character translation table.
6848    *
6849    * @param packed   the packed character translation table
6850    * @return         the unpacked character translation table
6851    */
6852   private static char [] zzUnpackCMap(String packed) {
6853     char [] map = new char[0x110000];
6854     int i = 0;  /* index in packed string  */
6855     int j = 0;  /* index in unpacked array */
6856     while (i < 3014) {
6857       int  count = packed.charAt(i++);
6858       char value = packed.charAt(i++);
6859       do map[j++] = value; while (--count > 0);
6860     }
6861     return map;
6862   }

6865   /**
6866    * Refills the input buffer.
6867    *
6868    * @return      <code>false</code>, iff there was new input.
6869    * 
6870    * @exception   java.io.IOException  if any I/O-Error occurs
6871    */
6872   private boolean zzRefill() throws java.io.IOException {
6873 
6874     /* first: make room (if you can) */
6875     if (zzStartRead > 0) {
6876       zzEndRead += zzFinalHighSurrogate;
6877       zzFinalHighSurrogate = 0;
6878       System.arraycopy(zzBuffer, zzStartRead,
6879                        zzBuffer, 0,
6880                        zzEndRead-zzStartRead);
6881 
6882       /* translate stored positions */
6883       zzEndRead-= zzStartRead;
6884       zzCurrentPos-= zzStartRead;
6885       zzMarkedPos-= zzStartRead;
6886       zzStartRead = 0;
6887     }
6888 
6889 
6890     /* fill the buffer with new input */
6891     int requested = zzBuffer.length - zzEndRead - zzFinalHighSurrogate;           
6892     int totalRead = 0;
6893     while (totalRead < requested) {
6894       int numRead = zzReader.read(zzBuffer, zzEndRead + totalRead, requested - totalRead);
6895       if (numRead == -1) {
6896         break;
6897       }
6898       totalRead += numRead;
6899     }
6900 
6901     if (totalRead > 0) {
6902       zzEndRead += totalRead;
6903       if (totalRead == requested) { /* possibly more input available */
6904         if (Character.isHighSurrogate(zzBuffer[zzEndRead - 1])) {
6905           --zzEndRead;
6906           zzFinalHighSurrogate = 1;
6907           if (totalRead == 1) { return true; }
6908         }
6909       }
6910       return false;
6911     }
6912 
6913     // totalRead = 0: End of stream
6914     return true;
6915   }

6918   /**
6919    * Closes the input stream.
6920    */
6921   public final void yyclose() throws java.io.IOException {
6922     zzAtEOF = true;            /* indicate end of file */
6923     zzEndRead = zzStartRead;  /* invalidate buffer    */
6924 
6925     if (zzReader != null)
6926       zzReader.close();
6927   }

6930   /**
6931    * Resets the scanner to read from a new input stream.
6932    * Does not close the old reader.
6933    *
6934    * All internal variables are reset, the old input stream 
6935    * <b>cannot</b> be reused (internal buffer is discarded and lost).
6936    * Lexical state is set to <tt>ZZ_INITIAL</tt>.
6937    *
6938    * Internal scan buffer is resized down to its initial length, if it has grown.
6939    *
6940    * @param reader   the new input stream 
6941    */
6942   public final void yyreset(java.io.Reader reader) {
6943     zzReader = reader;
6944     zzAtBOL  = true;
6945     zzAtEOF  = false;
6946     zzEOFDone = false;
6947     zzEndRead = zzStartRead = 0;
6948     zzCurrentPos = zzMarkedPos = 0;
6949     zzFinalHighSurrogate = 0;
6950     yyline = yychar = yycolumn = 0;
6951     zzLexicalState = YYINITIAL;
6952     if (zzBuffer.length > ZZ_BUFFERSIZE)
6953       zzBuffer = new char[ZZ_BUFFERSIZE];
6954   }

7007   /**
7008    * Reports an error that occured while scanning.
7009    *
7010    * In a wellformed scanner (no or only correct usage of 
7011    * yypushback(int) and a match-all fallback rule) this method 
7012    * will only be called with things that "Can't Possibly Happen".
7013    * If this method is called, something is seriously wrong
7014    * (e.g. a JFlex bug producing a faulty scanner etc.).
7015    *
7016    * Usual syntax/scanner level error handling should be done
7017    * in error fallback rules.
7018    *
7019    * @param   errorCode  the code of the errormessage to display
7020    */
7021   private void zzScanError(int errorCode) {
7022     String message;
7023     try {
7024       message = ZZ_ERROR_MSG[errorCode];
7025     }
7026     catch (ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException e) {
7027       message = ZZ_ERROR_MSG[ZZ_UNKNOWN_ERROR];
7028     }
7029 
7030     throw new Error(message);
7031   } 
7032 
7033 
7034   /**
7035    * Pushes the specified amount of characters back into the input stream.
7036    *
7037    * They will be read again by then next call of the scanning method
7038    *
7039    * @param number  the number of characters to be read again.
7040    *                This number must not be greater than yylength()!
7041    */
7042   public void yypushback(int number)  {
7043     if ( number > yylength() )
7044       zzScanError(ZZ_PUSHBACK_2BIG);
7045 
7046     zzMarkedPos -= number;
7047   }

7050   /**
7051    * Resumes scanning until the next regular expression is matched,
7052    * the end of input is encountered or an I/O-Error occurs.
7053    *
7054    * @return      the next token
7055    * @exception   java.io.IOException  if any I/O-Error occurs
7056    */
7057   public int getNextToken() throws java.io.IOException {
7058     int zzInput;
7059     int zzAction;
7060 
7061     // cached fields:
7062     int zzCurrentPosL;
7063     int zzMarkedPosL;
7064     int zzEndReadL = zzEndRead;
7065     char [] zzBufferL = zzBuffer;
7066     char [] zzCMapL = ZZ_CMAP;
7067 
7068     int [] zzTransL = ZZ_TRANS;
7069     int [] zzRowMapL = ZZ_ROWMAP;
7070     int [] zzAttrL = ZZ_ATTRIBUTE;
7071 
7072     while (true) {
7073       zzMarkedPosL = zzMarkedPos;
7074 
7075       yychar+= zzMarkedPosL-zzStartRead;
7076 
7077       zzAction = -1;
7078 
7079       zzCurrentPosL = zzCurrentPos = zzStartRead = zzMarkedPosL;
7080   
7081       zzState = ZZ_LEXSTATE[zzLexicalState];
7082 
7083       // set up zzAction for empty match case:
7084       int zzAttributes = zzAttrL[zzState];
7085       if ( (zzAttributes & 1) == 1 ) {
7086         zzAction = zzState;
7087       }
7088 
7089 
7090       zzForAction: {
7091         while (true) {
7092     
7093           if (zzCurrentPosL < zzEndReadL) {
7094             zzInput = Character.codePointAt(zzBufferL, zzCurrentPosL, zzEndReadL);
7095             zzCurrentPosL += Character.charCount(zzInput);
7096           }
7097           else if (zzAtEOF) {
7098             zzInput = YYEOF;
7099             break zzForAction;
7100           }
7101           else {
7102             // store back cached positions
7103             zzCurrentPos  = zzCurrentPosL;
7104             zzMarkedPos   = zzMarkedPosL;
7105             boolean eof = zzRefill();
7106             // get translated positions and possibly new buffer
7107             zzCurrentPosL  = zzCurrentPos;
7108             zzMarkedPosL   = zzMarkedPos;
7109             zzBufferL      = zzBuffer;
7110             zzEndReadL     = zzEndRead;
7111             if (eof) {
7112               zzInput = YYEOF;
7113               break zzForAction;
7114             }
7115             else {
7116               zzInput = Character.codePointAt(zzBufferL, zzCurrentPosL, zzEndReadL);
7117               zzCurrentPosL += Character.charCount(zzInput);
7118             }
7119           }
7120           int zzNext = zzTransL[ zzRowMapL[zzState] + zzCMapL[zzInput] ];
7121           if (zzNext == -1) break zzForAction;
7122           zzState = zzNext;
7123 
7124           zzAttributes = zzAttrL[zzState];
7125           if ( (zzAttributes & 1) == 1 ) {
7126             zzAction = zzState;
7127             zzMarkedPosL = zzCurrentPosL;
7128             if ( (zzAttributes & 8) == 8 ) break zzForAction;
7129           }
7130 
7131         }
7132       }
7133 
7134       // store back cached position
7135       zzMarkedPos = zzMarkedPosL;
7136 
7137       switch (zzAction < 0 ? zzAction : ZZ_ACTION[zzAction]) {
7138         case 1: 
7139           { yybegin(YYINITIAL); /* Not numeric, word, ideographic, hiragana, or SE Asian -- ignore it. */
7140           }
7141         case 15: break;
7142         case 2: 
7143           { yybegin(YYINITIAL); return WORD_TYPE;
7144           }
7145         case 16: break;
7146         case 3: 
7147           { yybegin(YYINITIAL); return HANGUL_TYPE;
7148           }
7149         case 17: break;
7150         case 4: 
7151           { yybegin(YYINITIAL); return NUMERIC_TYPE;
7152           }
7153         case 18: break;
7154         case 5: 
7155           { yybegin(YYINITIAL); return KATAKANA_TYPE;
7156           }
7157         case 19: break;
7158         case 6: 
7159           { yybegin(YYINITIAL); return IDEOGRAPHIC_TYPE;
7160           }
7161         case 20: break;
7162         case 7: 
7163           { yybegin(YYINITIAL); return HIRAGANA_TYPE;
7164           }
7165         case 21: break;
7166         case 8: 
7167           { yybegin(YYINITIAL); return SOUTH_EAST_ASIAN_TYPE;
7168           }
7169         case 22: break;
7170         case 9: 
7171           { yybegin(YYINITIAL); return EMAIL_TYPE;
7172           }
7173         case 23: break;
7174         case 10: 
7175           { return URL_TYPE;
7176           }
7177         case 24: break;
7178         case 11: 
7179           // lookahead expression with fixed lookahead length
7180           zzMarkedPos = Character.offsetByCodePoints
7181               (zzBufferL, zzStartRead, zzEndRead - zzStartRead, zzMarkedPos, -1);
7182           { yybegin(YYINITIAL); return URL_TYPE;
7183           }
7184         case 25: break;
7185         case 12: 
7186           // lookahead expression with fixed lookahead length
7187           zzMarkedPos = Character.offsetByCodePoints
7188               (zzBufferL, zzStartRead, zzEndRead - zzStartRead, zzMarkedPos, -1);
7189           { yybegin(AVOID_BAD_URL); yypushback(yylength());
7190           }
7191         case 26: break;
7192         case 13: 
7193           { yybegin(YYINITIAL); return URL_TYPE;
7194           }
7195         case 27: break;
7196         case 14: 
7197           // lookahead expression with fixed base length
7198           zzMarkedPos = Character.offsetByCodePoints
7199               (zzBufferL, zzStartRead, zzEndRead - zzStartRead, zzStartRead, 6);
7200           { yybegin(YYINITIAL); return WORD_TYPE;
7201           }
7202         case 28: break;
7203         default: 
7204           if (zzInput == YYEOF && zzStartRead == zzCurrentPos) {
7205             zzAtEOF = true;
7206             switch (zzLexicalState) {
7207             case YYINITIAL: {
7208               return YYEOF;
7209             }
7210             case 2910: break;
7211             case AVOID_BAD_URL: {
7212               return YYEOF;
7213             }
7214             case 2911: break;
7215             default:
7216             return YYEOF;
7217             }
7218           } 
7219           else {
7220             zzScanError(ZZ_NO_MATCH);
7221           }
7222       }
7223     }
7224   }
